# .mailmap — Canonical author identity for all SampleMind AI commits
#
# Git uses this file to rewrite author/committer display in `git log`,
# `git shortlog`, `git blame`, and on GitHub's commit pages — without
# touching the underlying commit objects.
#
# Format: Canonical Name <canonical@email> [Old Name] <old@email>
#
# All variants of the owner's email are mapped to the correct GitHub
# noreply address: 194328900+lchtangen@users.noreply.github.com
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Local macOS hostname email (git auto-detected when user.email not set)
